name: MakeUp Puzzle
description: Amazing puzzle with lots of MakeUp photos! The photo will be cut into 3x2 or 4x3 or 5x4 or 8x6 disarranged pieces. You must put all puzzle pieces at the correct position. Additionally you can use help button to put most of pieces at place. Also you can choose photos from your photo library or take it from camera and play puzzle.
